WEBVTT

00:00:06.280 --> 00:00:10.110
"JARNO" rider HMI with odometry.

00:00:16.290 --> 00:00:25.110
V2X based collision avoidance - LTE/5G.

00:00:27.230 --> 00:00:36.080
Automated vehicle sends position and route.

00:00:40.230 --> 00:00:47.130
Motorcycle receives vehicle route
and warns wider for collision risk.

00:00:55.090 --> 00:01:04.130
User interface for motorcycle speed and safety margin -
data received and processed from V2X gateway.

00:01:04.160 --> 00:01:12.290
Left turning in intersection -
motorcycle receives warning message.

00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:18.210
Connected road side unit

00:01:19.130 --> 00:01:22.260
Connected motorcycle

00:01:22.260 --> 00:01:31.260
Intelligence road side unit calculates collision
risk based on vehicle route and motorcycle odometry.

00:01:36.010 --> 00:01:40.030
Radar based front vehicle
detection in adverse weather.

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:52.010
Motorcycle estimate driver intention from rider
interaction (turning sign, brake force/acceleration).
